i)
Prepare PIP for the State Level Technical Institution;
ii) Providing inputs to PIP being prepared by the SNA relating to capacity building and research;
iii) Conducting capacity building and training for State and District officials;
iv) Conducting training for District Resource Persons;
v) Provide inputs for Branding and Marketing plans being prepared by SNAs;
vi) Provide

